data.description:
BACK ON MARKET - at no fault of the Seller!
Ready to sell! Warm and welcoming patio home in GWS for end-user or investor. 

Property has been newly painted (interior and exterior) and has newly painted decks in the front entry and side yard. Remodeled Main Bathroom, fenced courtyard for garden or pets. Walking distance to Mountain Market and across the street from Sopris Elementary. Views of Sunlight Mtn. Don't miss your chance to own in GWS! Easy access to Glenwood and Rio Grand Trail and Sunlight Mountain Resort.
